description:
On this week's mini-episode Doree and Kate kick things off with a question from a 19-year-old listener who wants to know if the urge to crawl out of your own skin goes away with age. Plus they discuss they best way to keep your feet soft and smooth in winter and get a product recc from a listener in Belgium.  

For more info and a list of products mentioned on this week's episode, visit forever35podcast.com. You can also join the Forever35 Facebook group, follow the podcast on Instagram and Twitter, and send them an email at forever35podcast@gmail.com. And now you can call them and leave a voicemail at 781-591-0390!

Theme music by Riot.
